Privacy Notice
Last updated: August 3, 2024
Welcome to Permutive. This privacy notice explains how we collect, use, and share your personal information when you:
visit our website at https://permutive.com (
“Website”
);
use our services as a Customer (
“Services”
);
provide services to us as a Supplier, and
interact with us in connection with our marketing activities, including any events or webinars we host or attend (
“Marketing Activities”
).
This privacy notice does not apply to personal information collected by our Customers from their customers and website visitors (
“Customers’ End Users”
) which they share with us when they use our Services (“Customer Data”). To learn more about how our Customers handle your personal information and how they share it with us, we recommend that you read that Customer’s privacy notice.
Please Note: When we refer to
“Permutive”
,
“we”
,
“us”
or
“the Company”
in this Notice we are referring to Permutive, Inc. and any relevant affiliate(s) involved in the processing activity, all of whom are listed in the “Contact Us” Section of this privacy notice.
We recommend that you read this privacy notice in full to ensure you are fully informed. However, if you only want to access a particular section of this notice, then you can click on the relevant link below to jump to that section.
